title: Esoteric Agenda
description: This is an excellent film which details the deception of the modern western world by the higher echelons of society.  This film traces the deceit back to the bases of religion and shows where religion was instituted as a base of control for the masses.  It then thrusts through to the modern day where 9/11 was used as a false flag attack in order to set the scene for martial law and the new world order.  Also goes into detail on the issues of flouridation of tap water, banking schemes, legal bindings in the united states, our subservience to the crown of england, skull 'n bones, the illuminati, an excellent compilation of all sorts of modern day conspiracies that are to culminate in 2012.
